Program: Outlook
Title: Special Programme on Kidnapping
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03kbrxs
Last Broadcast Date: Not available
A look at the worldwide rise in kidnapping for money or political ends. John McCarthy and Brian Keenan talk on the 20th anniversary of their kidnappings in Lebannon. Paul, the brother of murdered hostage Ken Bigley, Melanie, the daughter of currently kidnapped Colombian politician, Ingrid Betancourt and Brian Jenkins, expert on kidnappings are also interviewed. Presenter Heather Payton. Show less